  <div class="sb_box br-bg">
    <h3 class="right_title">
      <div class="position">当前位置：<a href="/" title="首页">首页</a> &gt; <a href="/about/?2.html">潍博之信</a>&gt; <a href="/list/?3_1.html">规章制度</a></div>
      <span>规章制度</span> </h3>
    <div class="clear"></div>
    <div class="active" id="shownews">
      <h1 class="title">第十三章  会议制度</h1>
      <div class="editor"><p><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">第一条</span></span></strong><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">为规范本馆各项会议及各类培训、讲座流程，统一会议管理模式，提高会议质量，特制定本制度。</span></span></p><p><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">第二条</span> &nbsp;</span></strong><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">办公室负责会议管理，所有重要会议须在馆领导批准后，进行高效筹办，并做好会议资料的整理、分发、立卷、存档等工作。</span></span></p><p><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">第三条</span> </span></strong><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;</span><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">会议分类</span> </span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:37px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">一、馆长办公会议</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:47px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">1<span style="font-family:宋体">、馆长召集并主持。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:47px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">2<span style="font-family:宋体">、馆长、书记、副馆长参加；特殊原因无法参加会者，须报请馆长批准，无故不得缺席。</span></span></p><p style="margin-left:47px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">4<span style="font-family:宋体">、讨论、决定馆内重大事务。</span></span></p><p style="margin-left:47px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">5<span style="font-family:宋体">、办公室负责做好会议的记录、整理工作。</span></span></p><p style="margin-left:47px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">二、馆务会议</span></span></p><p style="margin-left:47px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">1<span style="font-family:宋体">、馆长召集并主持。</span></span></p><p style="margin-left:47px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">2<span style="font-family:宋体">、每周二举行一次。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:47px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">3<span style="font-family:宋体">、馆长、书记、副馆长、各科室负责人参加；因特殊原因无法参加会议人员，须报请馆长批准，无故不得缺席。</span></span></p><p style="margin-left:47px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">4<span style="font-family:宋体">、研究、部署、推进馆内各项重大事务与临时性重要工作。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:47px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">5<span style="font-family:宋体">、与会人员须做好会议记录，及时、准确无误地向本科室人员传达。办公室负责做好会议的记录、整理工作。</span></span></p><p style="margin-left:47px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">三、全体职工大会</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;1<span style="font-family:宋体">、办公室召集，馆长主持。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">2、全体职工参加；因特殊原因无法参加会议人员，须按规定请假，无故不得缺席。</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;3<span style="font-family:宋体">、进行年度考核、民主评议、年度总结、重大决策推行等。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;4<span style="font-family:宋体">、办公室负责做好会议的记录、整理工作。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">四、其他临时性会议、培训、讲座</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;1<span style="font-family:宋体">、办公室召集。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2<span style="font-family:宋体">、馆内相关领导、科室人员参加。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;3<span style="font-family:宋体">、根据不同专题，开展相应活动。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;4<span style="font-family:宋体">、主办科室做好会议记录、留存会议照片，及时上报消息至办公室汇总存档。</span></span></p><p><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">第四条</span></span></strong><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">会议召开</span></span></strong></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">一、会议准备</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;1<span style="font-family:宋体">、办公室与相关科室做好会议前的议程安排，场所、坐席布置，会议的传达、签到，材料的撰写与分发，会议的拍照、录像、记录、会后的事项安排等工作。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2<span style="font-family:宋体">、如需用投影设备演示的会议，由物管科、办公室提前做好投影设备连接调试工作。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;3<span style="font-family:宋体">、物管科、办公室根据会议级别、性质备好会议用水及其他招待用品。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">二、会议纪律</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:47px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">1<span style="font-family:宋体">、参会人员须</span></span><span style=";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">提前</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">5<span style="font-family:宋体">—</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman">10</span></span><span style=";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">分钟到达会议现场</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">，</span></span><span style=";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">不得缺席、迟到、早退，</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">由</span></span><span style=";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">会议记录人员登记到会情况</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2<span style="font-family:宋体">、</span></span><span style=";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">所有参会人员在开会期间</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">须</span></span><span style=";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">将手机等通讯设备设置为</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">静音</span></span><span style=";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">或震动状态。会议期间，所有与会人员不得看报纸杂志、听音乐、接听手机</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">、相互交谈</span></span><span style=";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">等</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;3<span style="font-family:宋体">、</span></span><span style=";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">会议需要表决时，</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">采取民主集中制原则；</span></span><span style=";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">一经会议决议之事，应按期完成。对于需要在会议上讨论的</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">议题</span></span><span style=";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">，提前与参会人</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">员沟通。</span></span></p><p><br/></p><script src="/inc/AspCms_VisitsAdd.asp?id=467"></script></div>
      
      <div class="met_page">上一条：<a href="/content/?466.html">第十四章  保密制度</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;下一条：<a href="/content/?468.html">第十二章  物业管理</a></div>
    </div>
